    "title": "Junior Revenue Manager at Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Grow your career with Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Revenue Manager for our Surat team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited:\nYum! Brands India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yum! Brands India Advisory Limited!",
